<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Roland_A._Hernandez&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Roland A. Hernandez (page does not exist)">Roland A. Hernandez</a><sup id="cite_ref-Board_81-7" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Board-81" title=""><span>[</span>82<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
