<li><a href="/wiki/John_D._Macomber" title="John D. Macomber">John D. Macomber</a><sup id="cite_ref-Board_81-9" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Board-81" title=""><span>[</span>82<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Former_Officers" id="Former_Officers"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Lehman_Brothers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Former Officers">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Former Officers</span></h2>
